timing_enable_...r_clock_checks(25.10)  timing_enable_...r_clock_checks(25.10)

Name
       timing_enable_uncertainty_for_clock_checks

Syntax
       timing_enable_uncertainty_for_clock_checks

       {true | all | false | none | pulse_width | period | skew}

       Default: true

       Considers the clock uncertainty when performing clock checks.

       You can specify the following options:

              * true:  The set_clock_uncertainty command supports clock uncer-
                tainty for period, pulse width, skew, and separation checks.

              * all

              * false

              * none

              * pulse_width

              * period

              * skew

       Note: The  timing_enable_uncertainty_for_clock_checks  global  variable
       overrides timing_enable_uncertainty_for_pulsewidth_checks setting.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

